combustion.interpretation:
Sun is Combust (within 10° of Sun):

Effect:
Combustion weakens Sun's natural significations. The planet's energy is overshadowed by the Sun's powerful influence.

Impact:
• Sun's karakatva (natural significations) are reduced
• Planet struggles to express its positive qualities
• Results related to Sun may be delayed or weakened

Remedies:
• Chant Sun mantras
• Perform Sun remedies
• Wear gemstone for Sun (if recommended by astrologer)

retrograde.interpretation: Sun is direct. Planet functions normally.
